message.content: {"description":"Get swaps for a specific Uniswap V3 pool","endpoint_path":"/api/v3/swaps/{pool}","method":"GET","path_params":[{"description":"The address of the Uniswap V3 pool","name":"pool","type":"String"}],"query_params":[{"default":50,"name":"limit","type":"u32"},{"default":"null","name":"startBlockTimestamp","type":"Option<u64>"},{"default":"null","name":"endBlockTimestamp","type":"Option<u64>"}],"response_schema":{"fields":[{"description":"Block number where swap event occurred","name":"block_number","type":"i64"},{"description":"Unix timestamp of the block","name":"block_timestamp","type":"i64"},{"description":"Hash of the transaction","name":"transaction_hash","type":"String"},{"description":"Log index of the event in the block","name":"log_index","type":"i32"},{"description":"Address of the swap sender","name":"sender","type":"String"},{"description":"Address of the swap recipient","name":"recipient","type":"String"},{"description":"Amount of token0 swapped","name":"amount0","type":"String"},{"description":"Amount of token1 swapped","name":"amount1","type":"String"},{"description":"Square root price after the swap","name":"sqrt_price_x96","type":"String"},{"description":"Pool liquidity after the swap","name":"liquidity","type":"String"},{"description":"Tick at the time of the swap","name":"tick","type":"i32"}],"name":"SwapResponse"},"sql_query":"SELECT block_number, block_timestamp, transaction_hash, log_index, sender, recipient, amount0, amount1, sqrt_price_x96, liquidity, tick FROM v3_pool_swaps WHERE sender = $1 AND ($2::BIGINT IS NULL OR block_timestamp >= $2) AND ($3::BIGINT IS NULL OR block_timestamp <= $3) ORDER BY block_timestamp DESC LIMIT $4","tables_referenced":["v3_pool_swaps"]}
